{"tid":593443,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"STEAM 手提遊戲機《Smach Z》正式面世，可以出街玩 PC Games！！","createTime":"2018-03-15T03:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T04:10:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb6d907d144192d63eb557d4d3e74c1d0c2d601","tid":593443,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mc0IS4zuWsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMc0IS4zuWsc&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7ead4845\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mc0IS4zuWsc</a><br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a05d8cb40310c5fd6df70d8186069d36954a3e2","tid":593443,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9acba6465a57e80b3fe66b0656c5ba01fdc75b6f","tid":593443,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"聽得好辛苦"},{"pid":"ae8e08c1f037bc98a8e665498d7a876975e42b22","tid":593443,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"伏"},{"pid":"0c5c5a9d6e4c82dcdf4c9a11a51bcc22cec2c5f8","tid":593443,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:04:39.000Z","msg":"SMACH Z 這是一部能夠執行Steam遊戲的第三方手提遊戲機，將於3月15號開放預購，普通版售價699美元、Pro版售價899美元。換成港幣至少都要$5480，這樣的價格也能買一部電腦了，划不划算就看玩家的需求囉。<br />\n<br />\n不過這部遊戲機並不是第一次與大家見面了，在2016年就曾經與大家見過面，但當初的眾籌未能如期跟大家見面，引來些許不滿的聲音，因此這次開放預購，還是有些人保持懷疑態度。<br />\n<br />\n而且從規格來看，普通版本的硬體空間僅有64G，能同時安裝的大作數量恐怕有限，看來偏厚的設計，重量與手感上可能也需要玩家們適應。究竟這部「手提遊戲機」能不能夠符合市場需求，就讓我們觀察看看吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://game.udn.com/game/story/10925/3028264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.udn.com%2Fgame%2Fstory%2F10925%2F3028264&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=38b9bd43\" target=\"_blank\">https://game.udn.com/game/story/10925/3028264</a>"},{"pid":"b13050665d236d4e112b101ae7f7c6e0c88e0b3e","tid":593443,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/120553_b63b319a97b50cae9352f51b608a6086.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F120553_b63b319a97b50cae9352f51b608a6086.png&h=d3632ac1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5321615bae75e72f72bb1608da5230a0eba437a8","tid":593443,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"071d563a2ab3d1b01755cd1703955e3dbda50ddd","tid":593443,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"又厚又重不了"},{"pid":"088c770178d4d9b8b875e8de58866445ab549ad7","tid":593443,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"而且從規格來看，普通版本的硬體空間僅有64G<br />\n<br />\n裝一隻大作"},{"pid":"712863dbea1b3121624d67c3b0e7d370cf1d01bf","tid":593443,"uid":33905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"088c770178d4d9b8b875e8de58866445ab549ad7","tid":593443,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"而且從規格來看，普通版本的硬體空間僅有64G<br />\n<br />\n裝一隻大作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:07:49.000Z","msg":"一隻巫師就塞爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc328d067435799b639f91297f8166a8f3bd4000","tid":593443,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"最多得128G 裝兩隻Game就冇位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9e52392fe2128837f57ab0cfe309c544c5f16d","tid":593443,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc328d067435799b639f91297f8166a8f3bd4000","tid":593443,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:08:12.000Z","msg